OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe family of Dame Deborah James have
OL,8,Furged all UK political parties to
OL,9,Fcommit to a long-term cancer strategy
OL,10,F"to give more people affected by
OL,11,Fcancer more time with the people they
OL,12,Flove".
OL,14,FDame Deborah died in June 2022 at the
OL,15,Fage of 40, five years after she was
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with bowel cancer.
