OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe journalist used her diagnosis to
OL,8,Fraise awareness of the disease and set
OL,9,Fup the Bowelbabe Fund for Cancer
OL,10,FResearch UK, which has raised more
OL,11,Fthan #12 million.
OL,13,FIn a letter published in the Sun
OL,14,Fnewspaper, Dame Deborah's husband
OL,15,FSebastien Bowen, her parents Alistair
OL,16,Fand Heather James and her siblings Ben
OL,17,FJames and Sarah Wieczorek, said they
OL,18,Fare joining Cancer Research UK in
OL,19,Ftheir Longer, Better Lives manifesto.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/6
