OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe manifesto calls for the Government
OL,8,Fto publish a long-term cancer strategy
OL,9,Fwithin one year of the general
OL,10,Felection, to "drive earlier diagnosis
OL,11,Fand reduce inequalities in access to
OL,12,Ftreatment and care".
OL,14,F"That is why we are calling on all
OL,15,Fpolitical parties to make the upcoming
OL,16,Fgeneral election a landmark moment by
OL,17,Fcommitting to a long-term cancer
OL,18,Fstrategy for England, helping to give
OL,19,Fmore people affected by cancer more
OL,20,Ftime with the people they love," the
OL,21,Fletter said.
