OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"Sadly, we are not unique as a family
OL,8,Fin losing a loved one too soon to
OL,9,Fcancer. Many families across the
OL,10,Fcountry feel the same heartbreak every
OL,11,Fday. But it does not have to be this
OL,12,Fway. People affected by cancer must be
OL,13,Fat the heart of this general election."
OL,15,FIn the letter, Dame Deborah's family
OL,16,Fdescribed the You, Me And The Big C
OL,17,Fpodcast host as having "smashed
OL,18,Fstigmas around cancer" as well as
OL,19,Fbeing a "passionate advocate of the
OL,20,Fimportance of early diagnosis", which
OL,21,Fthey said "saves lives".
