OL,3,CDeborah James's family urge political
OL,4,Cparties to commit to long-term cancer
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThey said the strategy should include
OL,8,Fincreases in the NHS cancer workforce
OL,9,Fand investment in "vital diagnosis
OL,10,Fequipment to ensure everyone who needs
OL,11,Fit can access the right test, in the
OL,12,Fright place, at the right time".
OL,14,FIt comes weeks after analysis by the
OL,15,FBowelbabe Fund for Cancer Research UK
OL,16,Fannounced that cases of bowel cancer
OL,17,Fare set to rise significantly by 2040.
